calcMaxWidths

public int[] calcMaxWidths()
Calculates the maximum widths of the values in each column. A width is the number of characters in a cell.

Returns:
Maximum width of each of the columns in the table.

findNumCols

public int findNumCols()
Finds the number of columns in the table. Since the table may be ragged, this method will check each row will return the maximum number of columns found in the entire table.

Returns:
Maximum number of columns in the table.
